				\begin{document}$${\mathrm{\Delta }}E = \frac{{m^ \ast e^2F^2L^4}}{{24\hbar ^2\pi ^2}}\left( {1 - \frac{{15}}{{\pi ^2}}} \right)$$\end{document}where F is the field strength, m* is the effective mass, and L is the well width54.
